{"parse":{"title":"Anomalistics","pageid":7056993,"revid":849905252,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Fort_charles_1920.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cc/Fort_charles_1920.jpg/220px-Fort_charles_1920.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"295\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cc/Fort_charles_1920.jpg/330px-Fort_charles_1920.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cc/Fort_charles_1920.jpg/440px-Fort_charles_1920.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"596\" data-file-height=\"800\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Fort_charles_1920.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Charles Fort, anomalistics pioneer</div></div></div>\n<table class=\"vertical-navbox nowraplinks\" style=\"float:right;clear:right;width:22.0em;margin:0 0 1.0em 1.0em;background:#f9f9f9;border:1px solid #aaa;padding:0.2em;border-spacing:0.4em 0;text-align:center;line-height:1.4em;font-size:88%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding-top:0.4em;line-height:1.2em\"><small>Part of <a href=\"/wiki/Category:Paranormal\" title=\"Category:Paranormal\">a series</a> on the</small></td></tr><tr><th style=\"padding:0.2em 0.4em 0.2em;padding-top:0;font-size:145%;line-height:1.2em;font-size:175%;padding:0 0.2em 0.4em;\"><a href=\"/wiki/Paranormal\" title=\"Paranormal\">Paranormal</a></th></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 0.1em 0.4em\">\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\" style=\"border:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left;background-color:#ebebeb;\">Main articles</div><div class=\"NavContent hlist\" style=\"font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Afterlife\" title=\"Afterlife\">Afterlife</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Angel\" title=\"Angel\">Angel</a></